==生平==
雷鼎鳴於1964年畢業於灣仔[[東華三院李賜豪小學|東華三院李賜豪小學]]，與[[運輸及房屋局|運輸及房屋局]]前局長[[張炳良|張炳良]]為同級同學<ref name="《東華情深繫香港》新書發佈會 緣繫東華知名人士聚首一堂 憶說昔日感人情懷">[http://www.tungwah.org.hk/en/press-release/tung-wah-connecting-us-all-book-launch-ceremonynotables-reminiscing-their-affectionate-bonding-with-tung-wah/f 〈《東華情深繫香港》新書發佈會 緣繫東華知名人士聚首一堂 憶說昔日感人情懷〉，2013年2月]</ref>。後來於1964年一同入讀[[香港華仁書院|香港華仁書院]]<ref>{{cite news | title=小學升中考試揭曉 | url=https://mmis.hkpl.gov.hk/coverpage/-/coverpage/view?_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_hsf=%E5%B0%8F%E5%AD%B8%E5%8D%87%E4%B8%AD&p_r_p_-1078056564_c=QF757YsWv5%2BakvA8rFW5EhBx1LJWBXY%2B&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_o=10&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_actual_q=%28%20verbatim_dc.collection%3A%28%22Old%5C%20HK%5C%20Newspapers%22%29%20%29%20AND+%28%20%28%20allTermsMandatory%3A%28true%29%20OR+all_dc.title%3A%28%E5%B0%8F%E5%AD%B8%E5%8D%87%E4%B8%AD%29%20OR+all_dc.creator%3A%28%E5%B0%8F%E5%AD%B8%E5%8D%87%E4%B8%AD%29%20OR+all_dc.contributor%3A%28%E5%B0%8F%E5%AD%B8%E5%8D%87%E4%B8%AD%29%20OR+all_dc.subject%3A%28%E5%B0%8F%E5%AD%B8%E5%8D%87%E4%B8%AD%29%20OR+fulltext%3A%28%E5%B0%8F%E5%AD%B8%E5%8D%87%E4%B8%AD%29%20OR+all_dc.description%3A%28%E5%B0%8F%E5%AD%B8%E5%8D%87%E4%B8%AD%29%20%29%20%29&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_sort_field=dc.publicationdate_bsort&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_sort_order=asc&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_filter=dc.publicationdate_dt%3A%5B1960-01-01T00%3A00%3A00Z+TO+1969-12-31T15%3A59%3A59Z%5D | page=21 | publisher=華僑日報 | date=1964-07-17 | accessdate=2021-11-08 |quote= }}</ref>，並於1970年畢業<ref>{{cite news |title=香港華仁畢業典禮 狄恒神父暢談校史 |url=https://mmis.hkpl.gov.hk/coverpage/-/coverpage/view?_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_hsf=%E7%95%A2%E6%A5%AD%E5%85%B8%E7%A6%AE&p_r_p_-1078056564_c=QF757YsWv59f%2BqmPwqsIkJLiOfjPoWR%2B&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_o=1&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_actual_q=%28%20verbatim_dc.collection%3A%28%22Old%5C%20HK%5C%20Newspapers%22%29%20%29%20AND+%28%20%28%20allTermsMandatory%3A%28true%29%20OR+all_dc.title%3A%28%E7%95%A2%E6%A